      "content": "i think something is wrong with the world lol. like i was driving to work today and i saw the exact same red sedan pass me three times in a row but it was like... the same car. same dent on the bumper, same driver looking at his phone. it felt like a glitch in a video game or something. has anyone else ever seen stuff like that?",
