      "content": "a doppelganger? i dont think so. it wasn't just a similar car. it was literally the same car. even the way the sun hit the windshield was identical every time. and then later i saw a dog in the park that looked exactly like the one my neighbor has... same collar, same limp. it's starting to feel like things are just being reused. like the system is running out of unique assets or something. does that sound crazy?",
